Titolo: Illbleed

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Illbleed is a survival horror video game developed by Crazy Games for the Sega Dreamcast. It was self-published in Japan in March 2001, and published by AIA in North America in April 2001.Even though it was financially unsuccessful, Illbleed received a cult following for its notable combination of nonlinear gameplay elements and its "B movie"-style comedy horror theme, dialogue, and voice acting.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
